行业的新一波制裁&lt;/a&gt;可能会限制供应， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=ff49d6ed459546dea54f485ddd1967de&amp;amp;_e=7JTVORUV06v3yhvXq5ck5pGcB7Y56LgRGCLB-Pu_JWa2ZG9MLeDnREraQBoqCSa4FNS6z2P_xxWvec-AxHQHHBF0IHKESm7GlpWmsJ34-w9C4XUNHpwXEVVs3qzaorsJ8J1AAoxJDQPR-7jMPCUJ63LsclQDkY4ngBTiQNS4bqpPKbxFKfGkuRid_9B7ADA64ydncRjV61i09OXkQZiAGWTEEIF8k9m-e1di3Ae445kLS2sdQcFprEG1CkbySQLc0yhZDiRjs4m1pAb75vZmX0pafPKxvMBXYhN00STo-YeF9EcqqODxJbUZZv36LYeQC0f0gFq-64Bd3nJX42RKmQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;油价触及五个月高位&lt;/a&gt;。对于美元来说，前景更为乐观。高盛两个月内第二次&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=ff49d6ed459546dea54f485ddd1967de&amp;amp;_e=7JTVORUV06v3yhvXq5ck5o-C-22a-l1pB5TjATZXZIiFWtSd1ki-fYZEjoDoqJMJw77BC8L3KzkifNzcAst2XFzluQ76fJtNMUFZPKeTWASkrg6F8aB_FLWwo8XOGrJOhnRhi32cB5xFMHbsCWh0mTSRYRull1hnDaD_1NLwYatSzkYeMLYCHlSzG6uve3YyUEbeiRZbZ7YctF_PiUTDQ9MOfw-mDu1O9sQR1aMK1GGix5ibhJuuMw4dJ_3FuvtMQZdABgx90wW1KbETpPuMnAsB0hZHSHiIWktcgTwveuibTvBiHBYTOKO0CaWV4qs1UrG9GDHYxlqUb6YiLsLQzA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;上调美元预测&lt;/a&gt;，预计美元未来一年将上涨约 5%。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=ff49d6ed459546dea54f485ddd1967de&amp;amp;_e=7JTVORUV06v3yhvXq5ck5o-C-22a-l1pB5TjATZXZIgfwOv_4_MRwm47kQOc2JLpyFHWPvJwYQWPw9zqh8ZsJTbfA3xeIdo6kpa_Tv8drVPAbokRHY9zoRgne1kfoRmVZ70rNaNxBmvn12y_U22cP2J-jojIgOttUagbyR-vXb9X4TMJrMGOZcfgb0nwMVugAJvPuvqndVag44a1kYsNMQjT4xvw7vCqs9IJJbtF-3WF3K8X0Mp6-7x4ECwpmNADN6TF5Vcc_nOCdYskFcLqaUU2-0kCkH3QdLiclQV0bVbZF35Anr_hBfLefMuAo2_mqil3fvsXGD_v1YSqszMMdA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iAVzaT3o_lu8/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src=